HEADWORD: Heliogravure
<hw>He`li*o*grav"ure</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>h⟦eacute⟧liogravure</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The process of
